  </header>

  <main>

    <section class="hero" id="about">
      <div class="container hero-grid">

        <div>
          <div class="kicker">🕹️ Retro gaming van across Lincolnshire</div>

          <h1>
            Gaming parties with serious
            <span class="neon">90s energy.</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-copy">
            The Replay Van brings retro consoles, modern favourites, music challenges,
            competitions and pure nostalgic fun straight to your door — perfect for kids’
