          <div class="floating-badge">
            <strong>Gaming • Snacks • 90s Nostalgia</strong>
            <span>All brought to your door in one unforgettable party experience.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="section-head center">
          <div class="label">Choose your event</div>
          <h2>Not your average party hire</h2>
          <p>
            Designed for people who want something different, memorable and ridiculously fun.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-grid">

          <article class="service-card large">
            <div class="icon">🎂</div>
            <h3>Birthday Party Hire</h3>
            <p>
              Private hire of The Replay Van with multiple consoles and games for an unforgettable birthday experience.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card large">
            <div class="icon">🕹️</div>
            <h3>Retro Gaming Experiences</h3>
            <p>
              Step back into the 90s with classic consoles, iconic games and nostalgic fun for all ages.
