              <strong>Fun & Sim</strong>
              <p>Theme Park, music games and party challenges</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container showcase">

        <div>
          <div class="section-head">
            <div class="label">New update</div>
            <h2>Modern gaming is now included</h2>
            <p>
              After loads of messages asking if modern games were available, The Replay Van listened.
              Now parties can enjoy classic 90s nostalgia alongside modern gaming favourites.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-stack">
            <div class="feature-row">
              <div class="num">🎮</div>
              <div>
                <h3>The best of both worlds</h3>
                <p>Retro gaming for nostalgia, modern gaming for newer players, all in one party setup.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-row">
              <div class="num">🏆</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Competitions and prizes</h3>
                <p>Bring out everyone’s competitive side with challenges, games and prizes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-row">
              <div class="num">🚐</div>
              <div>
                <h3>All brought to your door</h3>
                <p>No venue stress. No complicated setup. Just book, turn up and play.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="image-frame">
          <img src="images/replay-modern-gaming.jpg" alt="The Replay Van modern gaming update">
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="reviews">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="section-head center">
          <div class="label">Reviews</div>
          <h2>Customers are loving it</h2>
          <p>Real feedback from people who booked The Replay Van.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reviews-wrap">

          <div class="review-main">
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            <blockquote>
              “Wow!! What can I say, my son and his friends had an amazing time in The Replay Van
              for his birthday. Nothing was too much trouble. The children loved the retro games —
              so did I — and all the different bits like the Tamagotchi etc. It was nice to have
              something different for a birthday party and it went down a treat. I would highly recommend
              The Replay Van.”
            </blockquote>
            <cite>— Kerri Fleet</cite>
          </div>

          <div class="review-side">
            <div class="mini-review">
              <strong>Perfect for kids’ parties</strong>
              <p>A different, exciting birthday idea with games, nostalgia and plenty to keep everyone entertained.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mini-review">
              <strong>Adults love it too</strong>
              <p>90s nostalgia, classic consoles and throwback games make it ideal for grown-up events too.</p>
